A great tool to constantly up your game in python is an app called Pythonista 3.
It is a completely mobile app that can run your python program in the app.
It is a great IDE for Python 2 or 3 and has some great features like converting from 2-3.
It also syncs across Ipad and Iphone so you can keep a project going and makes link apps so 
you can run your program from an app symbol on your screen. 
